{"word":"Arimathea","slug":"arimathea","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Arimathea</b> Called also Ramah. A town five miles north of Jerusalem.<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=57'>Mat 27:57</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=43'>Mar 15:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=51'>Luk 23:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=38'>Joh 19:38</a>"}]}